<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Adibas Z+</title>
  <style>
    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .start-button, .loading-screen, .hacked, .content {
      display: none;
      text-align: center;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    .start-button {
      display: block;
      background-color: #222;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #66fcf1;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #cfd8dc;
    }

    button {
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #667eea, #764ba2);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    button:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #5a67d8, #6b46c1);
    }

    .loading-screen {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .loading-bar {
      width: 0;
      height: 10px;
      background-color: #00ff00;
      margin-top: 10px;
      transition: width 2s ease;
    }

    .hacked img {
      width: 150px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #ddd;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Página inicial de producto -->
  <div class="start-button">
    <div class="logo">Adibas Z+</div>
    <div class="subtitle">Solicita las nuevas zapatillas del futuro</div>
    <button onclick="startLoading()">Descargar</button>
  </div>

  <!-- Pantalla de carga -->
  <div class="loading-screen">
    <p>Cargando...</p>
    <div class="loading-bar" id="loading-bar"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Pantalla de "Hackeado :)" -->
  <div class="hacked">
    <h1>Hackeado :)</h1>
    <img src="https://wallpapers.com/images/featured/personas-feas-35lj8z300gytzkyt.webp" alt="Riendo">
  </div>

  <!-- Contenido principal -->
  <div class="content">
    <h2>历史</h2>
    <p>
      凱文17歲，是一名職業替補球員。他對替補席的了解遠勝於球場。<br>
      有一天，他們終於告訴他：“熱身，你上場了！”<br><br>
      他興奮地繫錯了球鞋帶，跑了進來……結果第一次進攻就：<br>
      進球了！ ……一個烏龍球。<br><br>
      球場一片寂靜。教練用手擋住了他的臉。<br>
      凱文回到了替補席……速度比以往任何時候都快。<br>
      從那時起，他的綽號就變成了「對手的增援」。<br>
      這都是笑話:)
    </p>
  </div>

  <script>
    const loadingBar = document.getElementById("loading-bar");
    const loadingScreen = document.querySelector(".loading-screen");
    const hackedScreen = document.querySelector(".hacked");
    const content = document.querySelector(".content");
    const startButton = document.querySelector(".start-button");

    function startLoading() {
      startButton.style.display = "none";
      loadingScreen.style.display = "flex";
      loadingBar.style.width = "100%";

      setTimeout(() => {
        loadingScreen.style.display = "none";
        hackedScreen.style.display = "block";

        setTimeout(() => {
          hackedScreen.style.display = "none";
          content.style.display = "block";
        }, 2000);
      }, 2000);
    }
  </script>

</body>
</html>
